---
const pageTitle = "BADINGA Technologies | Secure AI Platforms for Regulated & Disconnected Environments";
const pageDescription =
  "We help mid-size defense and government-adjacent organizations deploy AI-ready Kubernetes platforms on-prem—securely, auditable, and without relying on public cloud.";
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg?v=2" />
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>{pageTitle}</title>
    <meta name="description" content={pageDescription} />
  </head>


  <body>
   <main class="page">
  <header class="header">
    <a href="/" class="brand">
      <span class="logo">B</span>
  <span class="brand-name">BADINGA</span>
</a>

    <nav class="nav">
      <a href="/">Home</a>
      <a href="/use-cases">Use Cases</a>
      <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <section class="hero">
    <h1>
      Secure AI Platforms<br />
      for Regulated &amp; Disconnected Environments
    </h1>

    <p class="subhead">
      We help defense-adjacent and regulated organizations deploy
      <strong>AI-ready Kubernetes platforms</strong> on-prem—securely,
      auditable, and without relying on public cloud.
    </p>

    <div class="cta-row">
      <a class="cta-primary" href="#contact">Request a Platform Assessment</a>
      <a class="cta-secondary" href="/use-cases">See how we help</a>
    </div>
  </section>

<section id="what-we-do" class="section">
  <h2>Your reality</h2>

  <div class="cards">
    <article class="card">
      <h3>AI stuck in pilot</h3>
      <p>
        You have models or analytics initiatives, but no secure,
        production-ready platform to deploy them in restricted or
        disconnected environments.
      </p>
    </article>

    <article class="card">
      <h3>Infrastructure risk</h3>
      <p>
        Your on-prem infrastructure is fragile, hard to audit, and tightly
        coupled to tribal knowledge—making modernization risky and slow.
      </p>
    </article>

    <article class="card">
      <h3>No platform ownership</h3>
      <p>
        Teams are stretched thin. ML engineers do infrastructure work,
        infrastructure teams block AI, and no one owns the system end-to-end.
      </p>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>


      <section class="section">
        <h2>A secure, AI-ready platform—delivered end-to-end</h2>

        <ul class="bullets">
          <li>Hardened Kubernetes for on-prem and disconnected environments</li>
          <li>AI/ML inference pipelines (no black-box SaaS dependencies)</li>
          <li>MLOps &amp; LLMOps designed for auditability and control</li>
          <li>Clear architecture, documentation, and handover</li>
        </ul>

        <p class="outcome">
          <strong>Outcome:</strong> A platform you can operate, explain, and defend.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="section">
        <h2>Why BADINGA Technologies</h2>
        <p>
          We focus on execution, not experimentation. Our work is designed for regulated
          environments where security, traceability, and reliability matter more than hype.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section id="contact" class="section contact">
        <h2>Request a Platform Assessment</h2>
        <p>
          A focused engagement to evaluate your infrastructure, security constraints, and AI
          readiness.
        </p>

        <div class="contact-box">
          <p class="contact-line">
            Email:
            <a href="mailto:contact@badinga.tech">contact@badinga.tech</a>
          </p>
          <p class="contact-line">Location: United States (remote engagements)</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <footer class="footer">
        <p>© {new Date().getFullYear()} BADINGA Technologies. All rights reserved.</p>
      </footer>
    </main>

    <style>
      :global(body) {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.5;
        color: #0b1220;
        background: #ffffff;
      }

      .page {
  max-width: 1200px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 32px 24px 80px;
}

.header {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: space-between;
  margin-bottom: 40px;
}

.brand {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 14px;
  text-decoration: none;
  color: #0b1220;
}

.brand:hover {
  text-decoration: none;
}
.logo {
  width: 44px;
  height: 44px;
  border-radius: 10px;
  background: #0b1220;
  color: #ffffff;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  font-weight: 900;
  font-size: 1.4rem;
}

.brand-name {
  font-size: 1.4rem;
  font-weight: 900;
  letter-spacing: 0.03em;
  color: #0b1220;
}

.nav {
  display: flex;
  gap: 18px;
}

.nav a {
  text-decoration: none;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: rgba(11, 18, 32, 0.8);
}

.hero {
  padding: 56px 48px;
  border-radius: 24px;
  background: linear-gradient(
    180deg,
    rgba(11, 18, 32, 0.04),
    rgba(11, 18, 32, 0.01)
  );
  border: 1px solid rgba(11, 18, 32, 0.12);
}

.hero h1 {
  margin: 0 0 18px;
  font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 3.8vw, 3.2rem);
  line-height: 1.1;
  letter-spacing: -0.02em;
}

.subhead {
  max-width: 72ch;
  font-size: 1.15rem;
  color: rgba(11, 18, 32, 0.82);
}


      h1 {
        margin: 0 0 14px;
        font-size: clamp(2rem, 3.2vw, 3rem);
        line-height: 1.1;
      }

      .subhead {
        margin: 0 0 22px;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        color: rgba(11, 18, 32, 0.82);
        max-width: 70ch;
      }

      .cta-row {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 12px;
        margin-top: 18px;
      }

      .cta-primary,
      .cta-secondary {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 10px 14px;
        border-radius: 12px;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 600;
        border: 1px solid rgba(11, 18, 32, 0.14);
      }

      .cta-primary {
        background: rgba(11, 18, 32, 0.92);
        color: #ffffff;
      }

      .cta-secondary {
        background: #ffffff;
        color: rgba(11, 18, 32, 0.92);
      }

      .section {
        margin-top: 44px;
      }

      h2 {
        margin: 0 0 14px;
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        line-height: 1.2;
      }

      .cards {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
        gap: 14px;
      }

      .card {
        border: 1px solid rgba(11, 18, 32, 0.12);
        border-radius: 16px;
        padding: 16px;
        background: #ffffff;
      }

      .card h3 {
        margin: 0 0 8px;
        font-size: 1.05rem;
      }

      .card p {
        margin: 0;
        color: rgba(11, 18, 32, 0.82);
      }

      .bullets {
        margin: 0;
        padding-left: 18px;
      }

      .bullets li {
        margin: 8px 0;
      }

      .outcome {
        margin-top: 14px;
        padding: 12px 14px;
        border-left: 4px solid rgba(11, 18, 32, 0.35);
        background: rgba(11, 18, 32, 0.03);
        border-radius: 10px;
      }

      .contact-box {
        border: 1px solid rgba(11, 18, 32, 0.12);
        border-radius: 16px;
        padding: 16px;
        background: rgba(11, 18, 32, 0.03);
        max-width: 620px;
      }

      .contact-line {
        margin: 6px 0;
      }

      .footer {
        margin-top: 54px;
        padding-top: 18px;
        border-top: 1px solid rgba(11, 18, 32, 0.12);
        color: rgba(11, 18, 32, 0.65);
        font-size: 0.95rem;
      }

      @media (max-width: 900px) {
        .cards {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </body>
</html>
